<div id="name">
My Research Topics
</div>

<div id="main">

I am interested in harmonic analysis and geometric measure theory. I am currently working on the following topics:<br>
<br><ol>

<br><li>
Decoupling theory for various geometric objects in the Euclidean space.
</li>

<br><li>
Marstrand-type projection theorems.
</li>

<br><li>
Maximal operators and local smoothing estimates.
</li>

</ol>



<br><br>Here are some of the academic articles I have written:<br/><br>

